Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘·密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  让人在意的睡不着觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:17.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}向着遥远前方的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.72,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你顺风而行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:27.60,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}追寻的答案不易找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}从开始就已明白才跨出的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:41.47,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}梦想的足迹  无数次绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}将描绘好的世界地图展开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.48,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}回响吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:54.66,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}闭上眼睛  心中的声音鼓舞着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:03:00.04,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}目的地还在更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.04,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}传递吧！风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:08.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}侧耳倾听  心中的声音满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:13.37,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}释放出耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.14,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}你化为蓝色的旋律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:43.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}此刻闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:51.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在这不归的旅途上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:57.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在片刻的安宁中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:03.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们怀着愿望入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:11.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}梦中的世界被光明照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:18.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}满溢的热情  寄宿着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:26.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}为了明天暂作休憩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:32.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我们现在在这里欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:38.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}它将在这旅途的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:45.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}一定会抓住命运的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:51.31,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}在此时此处描绘着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:56.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:03.06,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}共同前行
